      "content": "collective action is just a way to delay the inevitable, though. it feels like we're all just participating in this massive, slow-motion tragedy. if everything is truly destined to fail, then why even bother with the struggle of living? it feels more logical to just opt out now rather than wasting years suffering through the collapse. doesn't it seem more rational to just let go?",
